items.name: Google Chromecast
items.categoryPath: Electronics/TV & Video/Media Players & Recorders/Media Streaming Players
items.shortDescription: Discover a whole new way of watching TV with the Google Chromecast Device. This tiny device makes it easy to stream media services like Netflix, Amazon and Hulu straight to your television. Choose from over 200,000 TV shows and movies, 30 million songs or other radio and sports features. The Google streaming device is incredibly easy to use. Simply plug it into the HDMI port on your television set, connect it to your WiFi network, and start casting from your phone, tablet or laptop. The new Chromecast has higher video resolution and less buffering, with state-of-the-art WiFi architecture. The new integrated design also makes it even easier to plug into crowded HDMI ports without the need for adapters or extension cables. The media streaming device works with iPhones, iPad tablets, Android tablets and Android phones. It is also designed for tablets and computers such as Mac, Windows and Chromebook.
items.longDescription: <b>Google Chromecast:<br></b><br><ul><li>A better way to get video, music, and games to your TV</li><li>With Chromecast, your phone is your remote; simply tap the Cast button in your apps to start watching on the TV</li><li>Search, play, pause, and more, right from your phone</li><li>Unlimited entertainment, all on your schedule</li><li>Choose from over 200,000 TV shows and movies, 30 million songs, plus radio, sports, games and more</li><li>Discover thousands of apps at chromecast.com/apps</li><li>Mirror your Android phone screen or Chrome browser*</li><li>For apps that are not Cast-enabled, use your Android* phone or tablet to display exactly what's on your screen to the TV; you can also mirror your laptop's Chrome browser to the TV</li><li>Plug in and play</li><li>Get started in 3 easy steps: Chromecast works with the devices you already own</li><li>Plug it into the back of your HDTV, connect it to your WiFi network, and start casting from your phone, tablet, or laptop</li></ul><br> <b>What's New:</b><br><ul><li>Fresh new look, better performance</li><li>The new Chromecast has higher video resolution and less buffering, thanks to the state-of-the-art WiFi architecture</li><li>The new integrated design also makes it even easier to plug into crowded HDMI ports without the need for adapters or extension cables</li><li>Your one-stop shop to discover content</li><li>The Chromecast app has been updated to make it a destination where you can browse featured content across your apps, search for your favorite movies and TV shows and see where to watch them; plus, you can find the latest on new apps, offers, and features</li><li>Even more Cast-enabled apps to enjoy</li><li>Now you can cast thousands of apps across videos, sports, music, games and more...enjoy recent additions like Spotify, NFL Sunday Ticket by DirecTV, YouTube Kids, Google Photos and favorites like Netflix, HBO Now and Pandora</li><li>More ways to customize your TV screen</li><li>The same feature that allows you to transform your TV screen into a dynamic backdrop now has more customizable options</li><li>Display personal photos from Facebook and Flickr, or beautiful images from 500px and Getty Images</li><li>New choices for game night</li><li>With new Cast-enabled games coming soon like Angry Birds" Go!, WGT" Golf and Driver Speedboat Paradise, plus favorites like Just Dance Now and SCRABBLE" Blitz, you can turn your TV screen into a game board, racetrack, dance floor or trivia quiz</li><li>Everyone can play using their own phone as their personal game controller</li></ul><br> <b>What's in the box:</b><br><ul><li>Chromecast</li><li>Power cable</li><li>Power adapter</li></ul><p><br><b>Requirements:</b></p><ul><li>TV with an HDMI port</li><li>WiFi network</li><li>Google streaming device is a compatible computer or mobile device.</li><li>Supported OS and devices: Android 4.1+, iOS 7.0+, Windows 7, or Mac OS X 10.7, ChromeOS</li></ul><p>Availability and performance of certain features, services and applications are devices- and network-dependent and may not be available in all areas; items.name: RCA Viking Pro 10.1" 2-in-1 Tablet 32GB Quad Core
items.categoryPath: Electronics/Computers/Laptops/Shop Laptops by Type/All Laptop Computers
items.shortDescription: <p>Versatile and powerful, the RCA Viking Pro 10.1" 2-in-1 Tablet with detachable keyboard offers an adjustable and multi-faceted user experience to suit a wide range of uses. The 10 Viking Pro operates on Android 5.0 (Lollipop) and showcases the operating system's brand-new, critically-acclaimed visual design. The Viking Pro's amazingly clear, 10.1-inch high definition screen makes for an incredibly vivid and detailed viewing experience, and the impressive 1.3GHz quad-core processor is powerful enough to zip through applications and tasks quickly. Use the detachable keyboard and built-in trackpad to update your social statuses, compose emails and navigate the Web. When it's time to get down to business, open up the included WPS Office app to create compelling documents and spreadsheets. Effortlessly transition the RCA 10 Viking Pro into a stand-alone tablet by detaching the keyboard. Available in Pink, Sky Blue, Purple or Charcoal for a stylish, personal 2-in-1 tablet experience.</p>

items.name: Apple iPad mini 2 16GB WiFi
items.shortDescription: With this Apple iPad mini 2 16GB, you have easy access to the high-tech world right in the palm of your hand. This small but powerful device boasts a beautiful retina display that gives you vivid images and high screen quality. This Apple iPad mini 2 WiFi comes with an A7 chip with motion coprocessor. It also has built-in Wi-Fi (802.11a/b/g/n) with MIMO support so accessing the internet is simple and easy. It features a FaceTime HD camera so you can reach out to friends and family with video calls whenever you want. This 7.9" tablet is the ideal size for easy storage but with a screen big enough for you to view pictures and videos with ease. It comes with 5MP iSight camera with 1080p HD video recording so you can take pictures and create videos that you will be proud to share. This Apple iPad mini 2 16GB comes complete with iPhoto, iMovie, Garageband, Pages, Numbers and Keynote apps for your convenience.
